3","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 3"},{"id":20,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 4","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 4"},{"id":21,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 5","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 5"},{"id":22,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","location":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — photo 1","alt":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 1"},{"id":23,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","location":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — photo 2","alt":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 2"},{"id":24,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp","location":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — photo 3","alt":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 3"}]}},{"id":"itinerary","section_html_id":"itinerary","component":"TourTimelineSection","props":{"itineraryStops":[{"number":1,"time":"09:00","duration":"30分钟","name":"接送（济州市4个地点）","category":"接送——济州市酒店/集散点顺序","description":"**四个济州市接送点，覆盖主要酒店及交通枢纽**。按西→东顺序接客，确保巴士约09:50抵达含德——比游客尖峰人流更早，也为含德犀牛峰海滩保留最佳光线时段。Ocean Suites（08:30）→ 济州机场1号门1楼国内入境厅（08:45，**注意：与南部行程不同，使用1号门**）→ LOTTE City Hotel济州（08:55）→ 新罗免税店济州（09:05）。","image":null,"highlights":["四个接送点：**Ocean Suites（08:30）→ 济州机场1号门（08:45）→ LOTTE City Hotel（08:55）→ 新罗免税店（09:05）**","**注意：机场使用1号门1楼国内入境厅**（与南部行程的3号门不同）","约09:50抵达含德——**抢在游客尖峰人流之前**","请提早**10分钟**到达选定的接送点","出发前一天透过**WhatsApp确认**行程"],"timeUsed":["涯邑接送 ~09:00 — 5分钟","机场接送 ~09:10 — 5分钟","市政府接送 ~09:20 — 5分钟","东门接送 ~09:30 — 5分钟","沿1132号公路东行前往咸德 — 约30分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"四个接送点覆盖济州市主要酒店＋交通枢纽地带，无需让宾客横穿城市。西→东顺序接送让巴士约09:50抵达含德——比游客尖峰人流更早，同时为含德犀牛峰海滩保留最佳早晨光线时段。","smartNotes":{},"convenience":{},"visitBasics":{},"_role":"pickup"},{"number":2,"time":"≈ 09:50","duration":"60分钟","name":"咸德西牛峰海滩","category":"海岸","description":"**咸德犀牛峰海水浴场 (함덕 서우봉 해변)** 长期位列 **济州前三名海滩**,以 **白沙滩(主沙带约 500 米,3 段相连海湾合计约 900 米)** 与紧邻的 **犀牛峰 (서우봉,''形似牛头的寄生火山'') 火山锥** 形成的反差为标志,后者自沙滩东端直起。海水标志性的 **翡翠绿松石色** 来自浅海珊瑚沙海底对清澈海水的反射——这种近似地中海的色彩反差(在韩国少见)使咸德成为韩国国内拍照最多的海滨之一。\n\n海滩在夏季高峰期日承载力可达 **5 万人**,但春秋来访通常人潮不多。**犀牛峰**(可徒步攀登,约 1 小时登顶)在 **3–4 月披上油菜花黄**,登顶可远眺东向 **万丈窟熔岩洞一带** 的全景。**历史层次**:犀牛峰以西的海岸悬崖中藏有 **二战时期日本陆军开凿的隧道**——神风敢死小艇掩体与弹药储藏所,与城山日出峰的 18 个洞穴类似。这些隧道对公众开放(配有解释历史背景的标识)。\n\n海滩为 **济州 Olle 19 号路线(朝天 → 金宁)** 的中段,以蓝橙双色丝带标识。**Cafe Delmoondo (델문도 카페)** 坐落在沙滩边——大露台、海景视野,深受 Instagram 拍照与休闲驻足喜爱。**免费入场**;距济州国际机场 **20 公里 / 沿 1132 号公路驾车约 40 分钟**。","image":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","highlights":["**济州前三名海滩**——翡翠绿松石海水 + 白色珊瑚沙","**主沙带 500 米** + 3 段相连海湾(合计约 900 米)","**犀牛峰火山锥** 约 1 小时登顶——3–4 月披油菜花黄","**二战日本陆军隧道** 位于相邻悬崖——神风敢死小艇掩体","**Olle 19 号路线(朝天 → 金宁)**——蓝橙丝带标识","**Cafe Delmoondo**——大露台、海景、标志性驻足点","夏季高峰日承载 **5 万游客**;春秋人潮稀少","**免费入场**;距济州国际机场 20 公里 / 约 40 分钟","近似地中海的色彩反差——在朝鲜半岛少有"],"timeUsed":["大巴抵达+停车——约5分钟","主海滩+第二处海湾漫步——约25分钟","二战坑道外观参观——约10分钟","Delmoondo咖啡馆或海滩拍照——约15分钟","集合时间——约5分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"**以海开启上午的第一站。** 在济州市4个地点接送后，前往车程约40分钟的咸德海水浴场开启一天。轻松享受翡翠色海水、白沙与偶来19号路线的步行遗产之后，动线便延伸至内陆的城邑与东部尽头的城山·万丈窟。因是上午较早时段，即便夏季旺季也相对清静。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"hamdeok_seoubong_beach","kb_version":"1.19","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["Jeju Olle Foundation — Trail Course 19 official map","VisitJeju — Hamdeok Seoubong Beach","Jeju 4·3 Peace Foundation — Imperial Japanese Army tunnel records","Korea Tourism Organization — Top 3 Jeju Beaches ranking","Jocheon-eup local cultural office — Seoubong oreum trail records"]},"convenience":{"restroom":"海滩设有公共洗手间和淋浴设施","parking":"公共停车场(夏季收费)"},"smartNotes":{"photo":"犀牛峰剪影衬托下的日落是经典画面;犀牛峰山顶的航拍视角能呈现白沙湾的弧线","facilities":"沙滩前一带多家咖啡馆;附近便利店若干","tip":"比挟才或金宁海滩人少;东侧 Delmoondo 咖啡馆一带是热门日落点"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"24 小时开放(海滩);7–8 月开放游泳期,配救生员","closed":"全年开放","admission":"免费","walking":"轻松——沙滩平整;犀牛峰徒步为中等(有台阶)"},"images":["/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-01.webp","/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-02.webp","/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-04.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-01.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-02.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-04.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","location":"咸德西牛峰海滩","caption":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — photo 1","alt":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-01.webp","location":"咸德西牛峰海滩","caption":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — photo 2","alt":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-02.webp","location":"咸德西牛峰海滩","caption":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — photo 3","alt":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-04.webp","location":"咸德西牛峰海滩","caption":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — photo 4","alt":"咸德西牛峰海滩 — gallery image 4"}]},{"number":3,"time":"≈ 11:00","duration":"60分钟","name":"城邑民俗村","category":"朝鲜时代城郭城镇——重要民俗文化遗产（1423年创立）","description":"**城邑民俗村**是**朝鲜时代的城郭式城镇，始建于1423年**，持续作为县政中心**近500年，直至1914年**。村落在原有邑城范围内保存著**110栋传统建筑**，被指定为**韩国重要民俗文化遗产**。村落中心耸立著**两棵树龄逾600年的天然纪念物古树**。当地特色**五味子酒**可在村内家庭酿酒坊免费品尝。韩剧**《大长今》（MBC，2003至2004年）**曾在此取景。**免费入场**；以户外步行为主。","image":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","highlights":["**始建于1423年**——县政中心持续运作至**1914年（近500年）**","保存**110栋传统建筑** + **韩国重要民俗文化遗产**","**两棵树龄逾600年天然纪念物古树**矗立村落中心","**五味子酒** — 济州传统米酿酒，免费品尝","**《大长今》（MBC 2003至2004年）**拍摄地","历史伤痕：**1826年大火** + **1948年济州四三事件**破坏","**免费入场** — 仍有约250户人家居住","按照**朝鲜韩国风水原则**规划，典型县政中心格局","村落整体 + 多栋个别建筑获**独立遗产指定**"],"timeUsed":["停车+村落解说员迎接简介——约10分钟","走至古树+村落中心——约10分钟","参观韩屋内部（代表性民居2–3栋）——约15分钟","五味子酒酿造坊免费品尝——约10分钟","奥莱小巷散步+拍照——约10分钟","集合时间——约5分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"**本日行程唯一的内陆朝鲜时代遗产，也是地理上的转折点。** 它位于从咸德海岸前往城山的途中（表善内陆），把单纯的行车时间转化为有意义的一站。国家民俗文化遗产村落的石墙·茅屋与600年古树，为午后的火山·海女遗产增添了一段对比鲜明的“悠闲文化步行”，让一天不至于沦为单纯的拍照名胜巡礼，从而取得平衡。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"seongeup_folk_village","kb_version":"1.19","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["Cultural Heritage Administration — Important Folklore Cultural Heritage designation","Korea Cultural Heritage Foundation — Seongeup Folk Village historical records","VisitJeju — Seongeup Minsok Maeul","MBC Drama Archive — Dae Jang Geum (2003–2004) filming locations","Jeju Folklore Society — Omegisul brewing tradition documentation"]},"smartNotes":{"photo":"Stone walls (dolhareubang grandfathers), thatched-roof houses with smoke holes, and traditional doors are iconic Jeju shots","facilities":"Visitor information center at entrance; English maps available","tip":"Hire a free volunteer guide at the entrance for cultural context; respect that residents actually live here — don''t enter homes uninvited"},"convenience":{"restroom":"Public restrooms at village entrance","parking":"Free parking near entrance"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"Open 24 hours (outdoor village); shops typically 09:00–17:00","closed":"Open year-round","admission":"Free for general village; some private homes charge for guided visits","walking":"Easy — flat dirt and stone paths through the village"},"images":["/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-38-22.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-26.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-11-12-24-47.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-38-22.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-26.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-11-12-24-47.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 1","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-38-22.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 2","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-26.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 3","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 4","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 4"},{"id":5,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-11-12-24-47.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 6","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 6"}]},{"number":4,"time":"≈ 12:20","duration":"60分钟","name":"午餐（济州本地餐厅）","category":"午间休息——东济州本地菜","description":"在城邑民俗村与城山日出峰之间约60分钟的午餐时间。可在城山邑港口一带的餐厅品尝黑猪肉、鲍鱼石锅、带鱼等济州东部乡土料理。午餐费用另计（约₩15,000）。","image":null,"highlights":["**（冷汤生鱼片）**——东济州地区特色料理","**（鲍鱼石锅饭）**全年供应","**（海胆面）**可选——东海岸招牌食材","城山邑定位——午餐后**10分钟车程抵达城山日出峰**","午餐费用约**₩15,000**，现场自费","素食及清真餐需求请提前告知"],"timeUsed":["大巴前往午餐地点 — 约5分钟","点餐 + 用餐 — 约45分钟","大巴前往城山日出峰入口 — 约10分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"**联合国教科文组织核心行程之前的补给。** 在城邑前往城山途中的本地餐厅，以黑猪肉·鲍鱼石锅·时令海鲜等东济州乡土料理用午餐（餐费另计）。这是在进入全日最具活力的午后 — 城山攀登、海女潜水表演、万丈窟 — 之前补充体力的时刻。","smartNotes":{},"convenience":{},"visitBasics":{}},{"number":5,"time":"≈ 13:50","duration":"90分钟","name":"城山日出峰","category":"UNESCO凝灰岩锥——日出峰（三重UNESCO认定）","description":"**城山日出峰（城山日出峰，「日出峰」）**是一座**距今5,000年的萨托谢安式水火山凝灰岩锥**，拥有**UNESCO三重认定**（世界遗产2007 + 生物圈保护区2002 + 全球地质公园2010）。火口**直径600米、深90米**，周围环绕着**99块锯齿状边缘岩石**。步道：**单程0.8公里，爬升约140米，来回60分钟**，沿宽阔石阶攀登。**海女表演**每日在峰下岩石海湾**14:00（每日1场）**各举行一场（UNESCO非物质文化遗产2016年）。\n\n门票：**成人₩5,000 / 青少年₩2,500**，7岁以下及65岁以上免费。山顶是韩国**元旦日出朝圣**首选地——每年1月1日有逾5万人在黎明前登顶。","image":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","highlights":["**UNESCO三重认定**：世界遗产2007 + 生物圈保护区2002 + 全球地质公园2010","**距今5,000年** — 萨托谢安式水火山喷发诞生","火口**直径600米、深90米**，环绕着**99块锯齿状边缘岩石**（「石冠」）","**海拔182米** — 石阶步道来回60分钟","**每日14:00海女表演** — UNESCO非物质文化遗产2016年","门票：成人₩5,000 / 青少年₩2,500 / 7岁以下及65岁以上免费","春秋季开放时间 **05:00至19:00**（最后入场18:20）","**每月第一个星期一休馆**","韩国**元旦日出朝圣**首选地，每年逾5万人登顶"],"timeUsed":["停车+购票+底部简介——约10分钟","登顶观景台（0.8公里/高差140米）——约30分钟","顶部观景+火山口边缘拍照——约20分钟","下山——约20分钟","可选：在底部观看海女表演（每日1场，下午2点；恶劣天气时可能取消）——约10分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"**本日两处世界自然遗产中的第一处。** 午餐后登上城山日出峰（自选攀登往返约30分钟），观赏约5,000年前因水下喷发隆起的凝灰岩锥。攀登后随即衔接同一海域举行的海女潜水表演，再以同属2007年登录资产的万丈窟熔岩洞收尾，于一天之内完成“火山岛与熔岩洞窟”的叙事。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"seongsan_ilchulbong","kb_version":"1.19","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["UNESCO WHC inscription 1264 (Jeju Volcanic Island and Lava Tubes, 2007-07-02)","UNESCO Global Geoparks Network — Jeju (2010-10 designation)","Cultural Heritage Administration — Natural Monument designation 2000-07-19","Seongsan Ilchulbong official site (seongsan.kr) — April 2025 admission update","Jeju Haenyeo Museum — UNESCO Intangible 2016 inscription record"]},"smartNotes":{"photo":"Summit view of Hallasan to the west and Udo island to the north on clear days; haenyeo black-sand beach view from descending path","facilities":"Café (Fritz Coffee 1.3km away has best exterior views of the peak); ferry to Udo Island from Seongsan Port (1.5km/15 min walk)","tip":"All stairs but well-maintained — manageable in casual clothes; family-friendly with rest stops; sunrise visits popular but crowds gather pre-dawn"},"convenience":{"restroom":"Available at entrance and base","parking":"Large free parking lot"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"Mar–Apr & Sep–Oct: 05:00–19:00; May–Aug: 04:30–20:00; Nov–Feb: 06:00–18:00 (last ticketing 1 hour before closing)","closed":"Open year-round (weather closures possible)","admission":"Adult 5,000 KRW / Youth & Child 2,500 KRW (VisitKorea reference)","walking":"Moderate — 20–30 min steady stair climb (≈ 600 stairs); benches every few minutes for rest"},"images":["/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-07.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-08.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-09.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-10.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/seongsan-haenyeo-show-ai.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-07.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-08.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-09.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-10.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/seongsan-haenyeo-show-ai.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 1","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-07.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 2","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-08.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 3","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-09.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 4","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 4"},{"id":5,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-10.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 5","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 5"},{"id":6,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 6","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 6"},{"id":7,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/seongsan-haenyeo-show-ai.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 12","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 12"}],"liveStatusWidget":"haenyeo"},{"number":6,"time":"≈ 15:10","duration":"50分钟","name":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","category":"联合国教科文组织人类非物质文化遗产 — 济州海女文化（2016年）现场","description":"**济州海女文化**是**2016年列入联合国教科文组织人类非物质文化遗产**的活态遗产。本行程观赏的不是博物馆展览，而是**在城山日出峰下的海面上实际上演的海女潜水表演**。以海为终生劳作之地的**年长现役海女**，不借助氧气装备，仅凭*tewak（浮标）*自行潜水，您可亲耳听到她们结束潜水、呼气时特有的、似口哨般的“숨비소리”换气声。\n\n表演通常**每日两场（约13:30·15:00）**，依海况与天气进行，**观赏免费**。海女按潜深与潜水能力分为**下军·中军·上军**，上军可**一次屏息下潜10米以上**。目前现役海女**不足4,000人，大多在70岁以上**，亲眼所见的每一幕潜水，都是这一逐渐消失的遗产的记录。\n\n**遇风浪或天气导致表演取消的日子**，则以位于旧左邑下道里的**济州海女博物馆**（成人₩1,100，室内占比约80%，3个展厅）替代，在室内深入延续同一项联合国教科文组织非物质文化遗产。","image":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","highlights":["把**联合国教科文组织人类非物质文化遗产（2016）**以**现场潜水表演**而非博物馆呈现","在**城山日出峰下的海面**观赏现役海女实际潜水","不带氧气瓶、仅凭一只*tewak（浮标）* — 上军**一口气下潜10米以上**","亲耳聆听潜水结束时特有的**换气声（숨비소리）**","表演通常**每日2场（约13:30·15:00）**，**观赏免费**，依天气与海况进行","现役海女**不足4,000人·大多70岁以上** — 逐渐消失的遗产","**表演取消时改为海女博物馆**（成人₩1,100，室内80%，3个展厅）","与城山日出峰**步行·车程5分钟** — 无动线损失的自然衔接"],"timeUsed":["从城山日出峰前往表演场地 — 约5分钟","表演说明 + 就座 — 约5分钟","观赏海女潜水表演 — 约30分钟","拍照 + 提问 — 约5分钟","集合 + 移动缓冲 — 约5分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"**把联合国教科文组织非物质文化遗产以“现场”而非“展览”相遇的高潮。** 完成城山日出峰的攀登与观赏后，立即自然衔接至同一片海域举行的海女潜水表演（车程5分钟）。以刚刚看过凝灰岩锥火山地质（世界自然遗产）的眼睛，紧接着观看在那片海上世代谋生的海女的非物质文化遗产（2016），这一安排成就了东部行程独有的“火山 + 人”叙事。表演免费，且通常在午后时段举行，与动线也十分契合。**不过它可能因海况·天气而取消**，遇此情况则改以下道里海女博物馆的室内参观替代，**确保任何天气下都能体验海女遗产**。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"jeju_haenyeo_museum","kb_version":"1.29","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage — Culture of Jeju Haenyeo (2016 inscription)","Jeju Haenyeo Museum official site (haenyeo.go.kr)","VisitJeju — Seongsan Haenyeo diving performance","Jeju Special Self-Governing Province — haenyeo population census records"]},"convenience":{"restroom":"表演场地附近 / 博物馆内多处","parking":"表演场地·博物馆均免费停车"},"smartNotes":{"photo":"倚着浮标浮起的海女剪影，以及以城山日出峰为背景的海面画面颇具象征性。","facilities":"表演场地附近设有洗手间·停车场 / 取消时可使用海女博物馆的咖啡馆·纪念品店·英文导览","tip":"表演时间会依当日海况变动，由导游在现场告知。建议备帽子·墨镜等防晒用品。"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"表演通常13:30·15:00（依当日海况·天气变动）/ 海女博物馆09:00–18:00（最后入场17:00）","closed":"表演：遇天气·风浪取消 / 博物馆：周一·1月1日·春节·中秋休馆","admission":"潜水表演观赏免费 / 替代时海女博物馆成人1,100韩元·青少年800韩元·儿童500韩元","walking":"轻松 — 在海岸观赏，改为博物馆时为配备电梯的室内"},"images":["/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-16.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-17.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-16.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-17.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-16.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 1","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-17.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 2","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 3","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 4","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 4"},{"id":5,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp","location":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆）","caption":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — photo 5","alt":"海女潜水表演（表演取消时改为海女博物馆） — gallery image 5"}]},{"number":7,"time":"≈ 16:30","duration":"55分钟","name":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","category":"联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 — 拒文岳熔岩洞系统（2007年列入）","description":"**万丈窟（Manjanggul Lava Tube）**是约**8,000年前由汉拿山侧火山拒文岳喷发的熔岩**所形成的熔岩洞，**2007年与城山日出峰、汉拿山一同以“济州火山岛与熔岩洞窟”之名列入联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产**。它与城山日出峰同属**一项单一登录资产**，因此本行程在一天之内同时收揽**两处世界自然遗产**。\n\n全长约**7.4公里**（连同连接区段为13〜15公里），属世界最大级的熔岩洞，主通道**宽18米、高23〜25米**。因天顶塌陷形成的三个入口中，**仅第二入口约1公里区段对公众开放**，是进入后沿原路返回的**往返约30〜45分钟**路线。开放区段尽头矗立着**高7.6米、世界最大的熔岩石柱**，是万丈窟标志性的拍照点。\n\n洞内**常年维持11〜13℃**，夏季凉爽、冬季温和，但地面昏暗且略为潮湿，建议**备外套与防滑鞋**。万丈窟同时被指定为**国家天然纪念物**。门票为**成人₩4,000（团体₩3,000）/ 青少年·儿童₩2,000**，运营时间**09:00〜18:00（最后入场17:10）**，每月第一个星期三休馆。","image":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","highlights":["**2007年联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产** — 与城山日出峰同列“济州火山岛与熔岩洞窟”","**一天两处世界自然遗产** — 城山日出峰 + 万丈窟","全长约**7.4公里**，开放区段约**1公里**（往返约30〜45分钟）","开放区段尽头有**高7.6米的世界最大熔岩石柱**","主通道**宽18米 · 高23〜25米** — 世界最大级熔岩洞","**拒文岳熔岩洞系统** — 约8,000年前形成，国家天然纪念物","洞内**常年11〜13℃** — 夏日避暑地，建议备外套","门票**成人₩4,000 / 青少年·儿童₩2,000**，运营**09:00〜18:00（最后入场17:10）**"],"timeUsed":["停车 + 购票 + 入场 — 约5分钟","下行至第二入口 + 进入洞穴 — 约5分钟","开放区段1公里往返（至熔岩石柱）— 约30分钟","导览中心熔岩洞形成讲解 — 约10分钟","集合 + 移动缓冲 — 约5分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"**本日行程的第二处联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产，也是自然终章。** 在游览城山日出峰（三重联合国教科文组织凝灰岩锥）与海女潜水表演（非物质文化遗产）之后，位于金宁的万丈窟自然地落在从城山返回济州市的动线上。它与城山日出峰同属**2007年的同一项单一登录资产**，因此把两地放在同一天，便完成了“火山岛与熔岩洞窟”这一联合国教科文组织叙事。安排在午后较晚时段，可**避开正午暑热与团体拥挤**，并在户外行程之后，于**常年11〜13℃的清凉洞穴**中惬意地为一天收尾。若万丈窟因整修或天气关闭，则以同一熔岩洞系统的**日出乐园美川窟（替代洞窟）**替代，以保留洞穴体验。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"manjanggul_lava_tube","kb_version":"1.29","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["visitjeju.net (Visit Jeju official)","english.visitkorea.or.kr","jeju.go.kr/geopark","UNESCO Jeju Volcanic Island and Lava Tubes (whc.unesco.org)","Wikipedia Manjanggul (Dec 2025)"]},"convenience":{"restroom":"入口导览中心设有洗手间","parking":"入口免费停车场"},"smartNotes":{"photo":"开放区段尽头**高7.6米、世界最大的熔岩石柱**是标志画面，朝向宽18米·高23米长通道拍摄的透视照，规模感同样震撼。","facilities":"入口停车场旁的导览中心会讲解熔岩洞的形成过程 — 建议入场前观览10分钟。洞内没有小卖部。","tip":"即使夏季也请备外套（洞内11〜13℃）。地面潮湿且昏暗，宜穿防滑鞋。可能因整修而关闭，请提前确认到访当日的运营情况。"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"09:00〜18:00（最后入场17:10）","closed":"每月第一个星期三 / 暴雨时临时休馆","admission":"成人4,000韩元（团体3,000韩元）/ 青少年·儿童2,000韩元（团体1,500韩元）","walking":"适中 — 平坦的1公里往返，洞穴入口需下行台阶，地面略为崎岖潮湿"},"images":["/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","location":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — photo 1","alt":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","location":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — photo 2","alt":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp","location":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — photo 3","alt":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 3"}]},{"number":8,"time":"≈ 17:45","duration":"30分钟","name":"下车（2个地点+东门市场）","category":"下车——济州市集散点顺序","description":"**济州市三个下车点，方便返回酒店或晚餐**。下车点：济州市政厅∕涯月洞（约17:30至18:00）→ 济州机场（约17:40）→ 东门传统市场（约18:00）。东门传统市场下车后可自行前往晚餐（司机不陪同进入市场）；黑猪肉街距东门步行约5分钟。机场下车适合当晚有晚班机的旅客（济州国际机场末班机约21:30，17:40下车后时间充裕）。","image":null,"highlights":["三个下车点：**市政厅∕涯月洞（≈17:30–18:00）→ 机场（≈17:40）→ 东门市场（≈18:00）**","**机场下车（≈17:40）**——末班机前充裕时间办理登机","**东门传统市场**下车后可步行至**黑猪肉街（约5分钟）**","下车后为自由时间，司机不陪同"],"timeUsed":["大巴海女博物馆 → 东门 — 约25分钟","东门传统市场下车 — 5分钟","大巴前往市政府 — 约10分钟","市政府下车 — 5分钟","大巴前往机场 — 约15分钟","机场下车 — 5分钟"],"whyOnRoute":"东门市场下车 = 可选的晚餐停留。市政厅＋机场覆盖酒店区及晚班机旅客。距海女博物馆至机场约40分钟车程。","smartNotes":{},"convenience":{},"visitBasics":{},"_role":"dropoff"}]}},{"id":"day_flow","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourDayFlowSection","props":{"routeFlowStops":[{"name":"济州市+机场接送","type":"origin","theme":"出发"},{"name":"咸德西牛峰海滩","type":"secondary","theme":"海滩"},{"name":"城邑民俗村","type":"primary","theme":"传统村落"},{"name":"午餐","type":"meal","theme":"餐饮"},{"name":"城山日出峰（UNESCO）","type":"primary","theme":"UNESCO火山"},{"name":"海女潜水表演","type":"primary","theme":"海女非物质文化遗产"},{"name":"万丈窟（联合国教科文组织）","type":"primary","theme":"联合国教科文组织熔岩洞"},{"name":"济州市下车","type":"return","theme":"返回"}],"routePhases":[{"phase":"接送及海岸出发","duration":"约1小时","description":"济州市4个地点接送（08:30〜09:05）后前往咸德海水浴场。"},{"phase":"从海岸到内陆文化遗产","duration":"约2小时","description":"咸德海水浴场（60分钟）→ 城邑民俗村（朝鲜时代国家民俗文化遗产，60分钟）。"},{"phase":"午餐","duration":"约1小时","description":"城山附近本地餐厅 — 黑猪肉、鲍鱼石锅、时令海鲜。午餐费用另计。"},{"phase":"联合国教科文组织核心","duration":"约3小时","description":"城山日出峰（自选攀登）→ 海女潜水表演（取消时改为海女博物馆）→ 万丈窟熔岩洞（联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产）。"},{"phase":"返程","duration":"约1小时","description":"金宁 → 济州市，于2个地点及东门市场下车。"}],"routeShapeIntro":{"title":"行程路线一览","subtitle":"这是一条东济州环线，从东部尽头出发，在一天之内串联起岛上两处联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 — 城山日出峰（凝灰岩锥）与万丈窟（熔岩洞），二者均于2007年作为同一项资产登录。再加上属于联合国教科文组织非物质文化遗产的海女潜水表演。高效的路线安排可避开主要景点的拥挤。"}}},{"id":"details","section_html_id":"details","component":"TourFitSection","props":{"whyTourWorks":{"bestFor":["初次游览该地区的旅客","情侣","成人家庭","能够应付全日活跃行程的旅客","希望参观UNESCO世界遗产景点的旅客"],"lessIdealFor":["希望步行量最少的旅客","携带婴儿车的亲子团","当天还要赶航班的旅客"],"routeLogicSections":[{"title":"为何如此安排路线","icon":"route","iconBg":"bg-sky-50/80","iconColor":"text-sky-600","items":[{"label":"一天内2处联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产 + 非物质文化遗产","detail":"城山日出峰与万丈窟于2007年以“济州火山岛与熔岩洞窟”共同登录为世界自然遗产。再加上2016年人类非物质文化遗产的海女潜水表演，一天之内便能看到三重联合国教科文组织遗产。"},{"label":"真正的万丈窟 — 不再是替代，而是原版联合国教科文组织熔岩洞","detail":"过去休馆期间曾以美川窟替代，如今则亲身探访世界最大级熔岩洞、且拥有高7.6米世界最大熔岩石柱的万丈窟。"},{"label":"含全部门票 — 这一价位的价值所在","detail":"城山日出峰₩5,000 + 万丈窟₩4,000（城邑免费，海女潜水表演免费）— 两处世界自然遗产仅以₩9,000门票全数包含。"},{"label":"城山日出峰为自选攀登","detail":"往返约30分钟的火山口边缘攀登有一定坡度，并非适合所有人。也有无需台阶、可享相近景观的海岸环行路，可依体力自行选择。"}]}]}}},{"id":"practical","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourPracticalDetails","props":{"practicalAccordionItems":[{"id":"inclusions","title":"费用包含项目","preview":"全含入场费——此价位的最大优势","content":["空调小型巴士、英语∕中文双语持证导游、全景点门票（城山日出峰₩5,000、城邑民俗村免费、日出乐园∕弥天窟₩12,000、海女博物馆₩1,100、含德海滩免费）、燃料∕过路费∕停车费。","不含：午餐（约₩15,000）、饮料、小费。"]},{"id":"pickup","title":"接送与下车地点","preview":"四个顺序接送点；**机场使用1号门**","content":["四个接送点顺序：Ocean Suites济州（08:30）→ 济州机场1号门1楼国内入境厅（08:45，注意：东部行程使用1号门）→ LOTTE City Hotel济州（08:55）→ 新罗免税店济州（09:05）。","预订时选择最近的接送点。","出发前一天透过WhatsApp确认行程。"]},{"id":"walking","title":"步行强度与地形","preview":"中等难度。","content":["中等难度。","咸德海滩为平坦沙地。","城邑民俗村为土路与石墙。","城山日出峰火山口边缘攀登约30分钟陡峭石阶（可跳过）。","海女潜水表演在平坦海岸观赏。","万丈窟约1公里平坦往返，洞穴入口有台阶，洞内地面略为崎岖·潮湿（常年11〜13℃，建议备外套）。","必须穿包脚趾鞋。","全天步行约4〜5公里。"]},{"id":"cancellation","title":"取消政策","preview":"接送前24小时可免费取消","content":["接送前24小时可免费取消。","当天取消及无故缺席不予退款。","大风天气可能缩短城山登顶，但不取消全日行程。"]},{"id":"cave","title":"洞穴说明（万丈窟）","preview":"万丈窟为列入行程的联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产熔岩洞。","content":["万丈窟是2007年登录的联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产熔岩洞，已列入本行程。","开放区段约1公里往返（约30〜45分钟），尽头有高7.6米的世界最大熔岩石柱。","洞内常年11〜13℃较为清凉，建议备外套。","若因整修或天气关闭，可能以附近熔岩洞（日出乐园美川窟）替代 — 预订时请确认。"]},{"id":"children","title":"儿童与无障碍","preview":"建议10岁或以上，因为城山日出峰约600级石阶","content":["建议10岁或以上，因为城山日出峰的火山口边缘登顶（约600级石阶，可选但为全日核心亮点）及9小时全日节奏。","较小的孩子可以参加，但登顶可能太吃力；建议改选年度赏花或邮轮巴士行程（不含登顶）。","城山石阶及城邑民俗村步道不推荐婴儿车。"]}],"practicalWeatherStatic":{"today":{"temp":"—","label":"即时天气连动"},"tomorrow":{"temp":"—","label":"每日更新"},"_seasonalSummary":"东济州拥有全岛最通透的海景，夏季气温也是全岛最高。城山日出峰全年风力较强，建议备一件薄外套。","_seasonalTemperatures":[{"season":"春季（3至5月）","range":"8–22°C","notes":"四月初赏樱；含德犀牛峰斜坡油菜花盛开。"},{"season":"夏季（6至8月）","range":"22–30°C","notes":"炎热但海岸景点有海风。含德海滩海水色彩最佳。"},{"season":"秋季（9至11月）","range":"10–24°C","notes":"最佳季节——城山日出峰山脊视野最为清晰。"},{"season":"冬季（12至2月）","range":"3–10°C","notes":"城山日出峰山脊风寒效应明显。各景点人潮最少。"}]},"seasonalVariations":[{"season":"春季","description":"含德犀牛峰斜坡的油菜（芸苔）花——翠绿海水映衬金黄花海。"},{"season":"夏季","description":"含德海滩海水色彩最佳；城山日出峰日照时间充足。"},{"season":"秋季","description":"城山日出峰山脊全景视野最为清晰；城邑民俗村全年最具摄影价值。"},{"season":"冬季","description":"游客最少；海女博物馆在寒天尤为珍贵。"}]}},{"id":"booking_support","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourBookingSupportSection","props":{"bookingTrustItems":[{"icon":"check-circle","title":"当地持照合法业者","description":"持牌韩国旅游旅游服务团队，备有完整保险","iconBg":"bg-emerald-50/80","iconColor":"text-emerald-600","body":"持牌韩国旅游旅游服务团队，备有完整保险"},{"icon":"route","title":"路线专家","description":"精心设计的行程，而非千篇一律的路线","iconBg":"bg-sky-50/80","iconColor":"text-sky-600","body":"行程费用已含全部门票：城山日出峰（₩5,000）、万丈窟（₩4,000）、城邑民俗村（免费）、海女潜水表演（免费）— 现场无需另行支付任何费用。"},{"icon":"users","title":"精心控制团体人数","description":"精准控制人数的小型巴士格式","iconBg":"bg-amber-50/80","iconColor":"text-amber-600","body":"以小团迷你巴士（最多14人）从容游览城邑小巷、万丈窟熔岩洞与海女潜水表演。"}],"bookingSupportSteps":[{"timing":"即时通知","title":"即时确认","detail":"您将收到含行程摘要的预订确认通知。","description":"您将收到含行程摘要的预订确认通知。"},{"timing":"出发前12小时","title":"出发前12小时提醒","detail":"出发前分享天气更新及任何路线调整。","description":"出发前分享天气更新及任何路线调整。"},{"timing":"前一晚","title":"最终接送信息","detail":"确认确切接送时间及司机∕导游联络方式。","description":"确认确切接送时间及司机∕导游联络方式。"},{"timing":"行程当天早晨","title":"当日路线说明","detail":"出发当天早上根据最新现场状况提供简报。","description":"出发当天早上根据最新现场状况提供简报。"},{"timing":"行程途中","title":"景点逐一说明","detail":"每个景点提供即时现场讲解。","description":"每个景点提供即时现场讲解。"},{"timing":"行程结束后","title":"行程后支援","detail":"行程结束后提供后续建议及额外信息。","description":"行程结束后提供后续建议及额外信息。"}]}},{"id":"faq","section_html_id":"faq","component":"TourFaqSection","props":{"staticQuestions":[{"id":"q1","question":"真的能看到海女潜水表演吗？","answer":"可以。行程包含在城山日出峰附近海域举行的海女潜水表演观赏（通常在午后，免费）。表演可能因海况与天气取消，取消时则以下道里海女博物馆的室内参观替代，确保能体验海女遗产。"},{"id":"q2","question":"可以跳过城山日出峰的火山口攀登吗？","answer":"可以。有无需台阶也能拍到相近角度的海岸环行路。火山口攀登（往返约0.8公里，约30分钟）为自选项目，可依体力自行决定。"},{"id":"q3","question":"与济州南部联合国教科文组织行程有何区别？","answer":"这是同一家旅行社的行程。南部行程包含汉拿山的오름、山茶花园、天帝渊瀑布、柱状节理、O''sulloc茶园。东部行程则以城山日出峰、城邑民俗村、万丈窟、海女潜水表演为主。"},{"id":"q4","question":"万丈窟关闭的日子怎么办？","answer":"万丈窟是列入行程的联合国教科文组织世界自然遗产熔岩洞。但若因整修或天气（暴雨等）关闭，则以同一熔岩洞系统的日出乐园美川窟等附近洞穴替代，以保留洞穴体验。"},{"id":"q5","question":"是否包含午餐？","answer":"不包含。午餐费用另计（约₩15,000），由导游为您推荐当地美食。"}]}},{"id":"reviews","section_html_id":"reviews","component":"TourReviewsSection","props":{"guestReviews":[],"reviewsSummary":{"averageRating":0,"totalReviews":0,"ratingDistribution":[{"stars":5,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":4,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":3,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":2,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":1,"count":0,"percentage":0}],"highlights":[]},"reviewsAttribution":"评价汇总来自当地团队在市场参考资料的页面；可在该页面查看具体游客评价。"}},{"id":"sticky_booking","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourStickyBookingBar","props":{"note":"可订状态将在支付步骤中确认。","price":{"amountLabel":"47","originalPriceUsd":59,"salePriceUsd":47,"discountPercent":20,"currency":"USD","per":"person"}}}],"itinerary_variants":[],"_publication":{"schema_version":"v4_canonical","last_modified":"2026-04-28","version_history":["v11","v12","v13","v14","v15","v15.2"],"fix_passes":{"v12":"P0+P1 — pickup_dropoff Schema A unification, routeFlowStops type-based, competing_products → internal slugs, anchor_poi_keys aligned","v13":"P1.5 — pickup_dropoff Schema A.2 → A.1; practicalAccordionItems / routePhases / seasonalVariations unified to V4 canonical (no Tailwind in data)","v14":"P2 — _publication uniform; duration formatting standardized; glanceItems Duration added where missing","v15":"P3 round 1 — SEO trim. seo.pageTitle rewritten to ≤65 chars (was 14/25 over 70); seo.metaDescription rewritten to ≤168 chars (was 25/25 over 170). primaryKeywords and ogImage unchanged. Hero/OG images, POI verification, review imports, and routePhases enrichment deferred to later P3 rounds.","v15.2_charter_consolidation":"Removed \"jeju-popular-sightseeing-private-car-charter-tour\" from competing_products per Jason''s one-charter-per-region rule (jeju-island-private-car-charter-tour remains as canonical Jeju charter).","v17_schema_unification":{"date":"2026-04-28","description":"Phase 1: Standardized matching_profile scores to the current 0-1 float scale used by match_tours.matching_profile.","fields_converted":43,"fields_skipped":0,"fields_already_float":0},"v17_batch2_enhancement":{"date":"2026-04-28","description":"Batch 2 deep enhancement — descriptions raised to 700-1100+ chars; KB-backed visitBasics/convenience/smartNotes/_poi_meta on all attraction stops; product profile recalibrated with verified-fact 0-1 float scores (replacing Phase 1 mechanical conversion).","_score_audit":{"_methodology":"0-1 float scale. Each score grounded in verified facts.","deltas_applied":{"unesco_fit":{"old":1,"new":1,"reasoning":"VERIFIED 1.0 — this tour is correctly named ''eastern UNESCO loop'': Seongsan = UNESCO World Heritage (Jeju Volcanic Island & Lava Tubes 2007), Haenyeo Museum = UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage (haenyeo culture 2016). Tour covers BOTH UNESCO categories. Strongest UNESCO-fit tour in catalogue."},"intangible_heritage_fit":{"old":1,"new":1,"reasoning":"VERIFIED 1.0 — Haenyeo Museum is the dedicated UNESCO ICH interpretation center; Seongsan haenyeo demonstration at 14:00 (1 show/day) is the live UNESCO ICH performance; Seongeup Folk Village preserves Joseon-period intangible folkways. 3 of 5 attractions carry intangible-heritage value. Highest possible score."},"walking_level":{"old":0.8,"new":0.65,"reasoning":"DOWNGRADED 0.8→0.65 with verified totals: Hamdeok beach 0.5 km flat (sand + boardwalk), Seongeup ~1 km flat olle, Micheon Cave 365 m flat (leveled), Seongsan 0.8 km + 140 m gain (the only stair-heavy stop), Haenyeo Museum 100% indoor flat. Total ~3 km + only Seongsan has elevation. Tour 1 (east-signature) walks more (Seopjikoji 2.1 km extra). Verified moderate walking = 0.65 not 0.8."},"young_kids_fit":{"old":1,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"DOWNGRADED 1.0→0.75: Hamdeok beach + leveled Micheon Cave + indoor Haenyeo Museum + Seongeup folk village = 4 of 5 kid-friendly. ONLY Seongsan''s 300-500 steps challenge under-7s. Mechanical 1.0 was overstated; verified 0.75 is honest."},"stroller_fit":{"old":0.4,"new":0.5,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.4→0.50: Hamdeok flat + Micheon Cave LEVELED FLOOR (verified — vs Manjanggul''s uneven natural floor) + Haenyeo Museum 100% accessible + Seongeup main alleys + ONLY Seongsan stairs unsuitable. 4/5 stroller-friendly = 0.50 not the previous 0.4. Specifically chose Micheon vs Manjanggul for accessibility."},"mobility_friendly_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.65,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.65: Verified 4 of 5 stops mobility-friendly (Hamdeok flat, Micheon leveled, Haenyeo Museum elevators, Seongeup flat alleys), only Seongsan summit not accessible. The choice of Micheon Cave instead of Manjanggul specifically supports this."},"weather_sensitivity":{"old":1,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"DOWNGRADED 1.0→0.75 — verified: Haenyeo Museum 100% indoor, Micheon Cave 100% indoor and stable temperature year-round, Seongeup hanok have shelter. Only Hamdeok and Seongsan are weather-exposed. The ''all UNESCO'' name made the prior score look high, but indoor ratio is actually reasonable. Mechanical 1.0 overstated."},"indoor_ratio":{"old":0.1,"new":0.4,"reasoning":"MAJOR CORRECTION: Verified breakdown — Hamdeok 100% outdoor, Seongeup ~30% indoor (visiting hanok interiors), Micheon Cave 100% indoor, Seongsan 5% indoor (visitor center only), Haenyeo Museum 100% indoor. Time-weighted indoor ratio ~40%, NOT the previous 10%. Correcting a documentation error."},"rain_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.75: With Micheon Cave (indoor), Haenyeo Museum (indoor), and Seongeup hanok interiors as rain refuges, this tour holds up MUCH better in rain than the mechanical 0.6 implied. Hamdeok and Seongsan suffer in rain but the rest is fine. Verified."},"iconic_landmark_fit":{"old":1,"new":0.85,"reasoning":"VERIFIED 0.85: Seongsan = universally iconic (triple UNESCO crown). Hamdeok = Top 3 Jeju beach. Seongeup + Haenyeo Museum = nationally significant culture (UNESCO ICH for Haenyeo). Micheon Cave = secondary lava tube. 0.85 — strong but not all 5 universally iconic."},"value_for_money_fit":{"old":1,"new":0.85,"reasoning":"Verified fees: Hamdeok free + Seongeup free + Micheon ₩12,000 + Seongsan ₩2,000 + Haenyeo Museum ₩1,100 = ~₩15,100/adult. Reasonable but Ilchul Land at ₩12,000 is the big driver. 0.85 calibrated."},"senior_fit":{"old":0.4,"new":0.55,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.4→0.55: With Hamdeok beach walk (flat), Micheon leveled cave, Seongeup flat alleys, Haenyeo Museum accessible — 4 of 5 stops fully senior-accessible. Only Seongsan summit excludes seniors with mobility issues (alternative: stay at base for haenyeo demo). Verified ≥0.55, much better than 0.4."},"senior_active_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.75: For active seniors, all 5 stops are achievable (Seongsan rest stops + benches make 45-60 min summit reasonable). Cultural depth (UNESCO + 600-year village + 400-year haenyeo tradition) very strong appeal for senior travelers. 0.75 verified."},"senior_general_fit":{"old":0.4,"new":0.55,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.4→0.55: Same logic — 4/5 stops accessible to general senior population (alternative for Seongsan = stay at base for haenyeo demonstration). 0.55 calibrated."},"beach_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.85,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.85: Hamdeok IS the dedicated beach stop — Top 3 Jeju beach (verified VisitKorea ranking). 0.6 understates this; 0.85 reflects beach as a primary tour theme."},"culture_level":{"old":1,"new":0.95,"reasoning":"Slight DOWNGRADE 1.0→0.95: Verified 3 strong cultural anchors (Seongeup 600-year town + Haenyeo 400-year tradition + Seongsan haenyeo demo). Hamdeok is recreational not cultural. 0.95 (vs east-signature''s lower) — still very strong."}}},"stops_enhanced":6,"sources":["VisitKorea","Wikipedia","UNESCO","Visit Jeju","Inside Jeju","Jeju Tourism Organization","AllTrails"]},"v17_fix1_indoor_ratio_correction":{"date":"2026-04-28","description":"Jason correction: Micheon Cave and Seongeup Folk Village are 70% outdoor. Recalculated tour-level indoor_ratio with time-weighted attraction durations and adjusted dependent fields.","computation":{"stops_time_weighted":{"hamdeok_seoubong_beach":"45min × 0.00 indoor = 0.00","seongeup_folk_village":"75min × 0.30 indoor = 22.50 (corrected from 0.50)","ilchulland_micheon_cave":"60min × 0.30 indoor = 18.00 (corrected from 0.60)","seongsan_ilchulbong":"90min × 0.05 indoor = 4.50","jeju_haenyeo_museum":"60min × 1.00 indoor = 60.00","total_indoor_min":105,"total_substantive_min":330,"computed_indoor_ratio":0.32}},"changes":{"indoor_ratio":{"old":0.4,"new":0.3,"reason":"Recalculated 105/330 = 0.32, rounded to 0.30"},"rain_fit":{"old":0.75,"new":0.55,"reason":"Only Haenyeo Museum is full refuge; Seongeup and Micheon mostly outdoor; Hamdeok and Seongsan rain-bad"},"weather_sensitivity":{"old":0.75,"new":0.7,"reason":"Still has Haenyeo Museum as anchor refuge but 70% of stop time is weather-exposed"}}}}},"liveStatusSection":"haenyeo"}'::jsonb
