物館） — gallery image 2"},{"id":19,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 3","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 3"},{"id":20,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 4","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 4"},{"id":21,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 5","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 5"},{"id":22,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","location":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — photo 1","alt":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 1"},{"id":23,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","location":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — photo 2","alt":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 2"},{"id":24,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp","location":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — photo 3","alt":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 3"}]}},{"id":"itinerary","section_html_id":"itinerary","component":"TourTimelineSection","props":{"itineraryStops":[{"number":1,"time":"09:00","duration":"30分鐘","name":"接送（濟州市4個地點）","category":"接送——濟州市飯店/集散點順序","description":"**四個濟州市接送點，覆蓋主要飯店及交通樞紐**。按西→東順序接客，確保巴士約09:50抵達含德——比遊客尖峰人流更早，也為含德犀牛峰海灘保留最佳光線時段。Ocean Suites（08:30）→ 濟州機場1號門1樓國內入境廳（08:45，**注意：與南部行程不同，使用1號門**）→ LOTTE City Hotel濟州（08:55）→ 新羅免稅店濟州（09:05）。","image":null,"highlights":["四個接送點：**Ocean Suites（08:30）→ 濟州機場1號門（08:45）→ LOTTE City Hotel（08:55）→ 新羅免稅店（09:05）**","**注意：機場使用1號門1樓國內入境廳**（與南部行程的3號門不同）","約09:50抵達含德——**搶在遊客尖峰人流之前**","請提早**10分鐘**到達選定的接送點","出發前一天透過**WhatsApp確認**行程"],"timeUsed":["涯邑接送 ~09:00 — 5分鐘","機場接送 ~09:10 — 5分鐘","市政府接送 ~09:20 — 5分鐘","東門接送 ~09:30 — 5分鐘","沿1132號公路東行前往鹹德 — 約30分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"四個接送點覆蓋濟州市主要飯店＋交通樞紐地帶，無需讓賓客橫穿城市。西→東順序接送讓巴士約09:50抵達含德——比遊客尖峰人流更早，同時為含德犀牛峰海灘保留最佳早晨光線時段。","smartNotes":{},"convenience":{},"visitBasics":{},"_role":"pickup"},{"number":2,"time":"≈ 09:50","duration":"60分鐘","name":"鹹德西牛峰海灘","category":"海岸","description":"**咸德犀牛峰海水浴場（함덕 서우봉 해변）** 長期穩居 **濟州 3 大海灘** 之列，標誌性畫面是 **白沙灘（主沙灘約 500 公尺，3 個相連海灣總長約 900 公尺）** 與東端緊臨而起的 **火山寄生岳「犀牛峰」（서우봉，意為「酷似牛頭的寄生火山錐」）** 之間的鮮明對比。海水的招牌 **翡翠綠松石色** 來自淺海珊瑚砂海床透過清澈海水反射的折射效果——這種媲美地中海的色彩對比在韓國相當罕見，正是讓咸德成為國內最受拍攝青睞的海灘之一的關鍵。\n\n海灘在夏季旺季可消化 **每日 5 萬人次** 來客量，但春秋造訪通常人潮稀疏。**犀牛峰**（登頂約 1 小時）在 **春季 3–4 月披上油菜花黃色山坡**，並提供 **遠眺東方萬丈窟熔岩管區的全景**。**歷史層次**：犀牛峰西側海蝕崖中保留 **二戰殖民時期日本帝國陸軍開鑿的坑道**——神風特攻艇藏匿坑與彈藥庫，與城山日出峰的 18 個洞窟性質相似。\n\n坑道現已對公眾開放（設有解說標示說明歷史脈絡）。本沙灘是 **濟州 Olle 步道 19 號路線（朝天 → 金寧）** 的核心段落，沿途有藍橙相間的緞帶標示。**Cafe Delmoondo（델문도 카페）** 是海灘的代表咖啡館——擁有大型海景露台，是熱門的 IG 打卡與休憩點。**免費入場**；距濟州國際機場約 **20 公里／40 分鐘車程**，沿 1132 號公路抵達。","image":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","highlights":["**濟州 3 大海灘**——翡翠綠松石海水＋白色珊瑚砂","**主沙灘 500 公尺**＋3 個相連海灣（總長約 900 公尺）","**犀牛峰寄生火山錐** 約 1 小時登頂——3–4 月油菜花黃色山坡","**二戰日本帝國陸軍坑道** 位於相鄰崖壁——神風特攻艇藏匿坑","**Olle 步道 19 號路線（朝天 → 金寧）**——藍橙緞帶路標","**Cafe Delmoondo**——大型海濱露台，標誌性歇腳點","夏季旺季每日最多 **5 萬人次**；春秋人潮稀疏","**免費入場**；距濟州國際機場 20 公里／約 40 分鐘","媲美地中海的色彩對比——韓半島上極為罕見"],"timeUsed":["大巴抵達+停車——約5分鐘","主海灘+第二處海灣漫步——約25分鐘","二戰坑道外觀參觀——約10分鐘","Delmoondo咖啡館或海灘拍照——約15分鐘","集合時間——約5分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"**以大海揭開上午的第一站。** 濟州市4個地點接送後，前往車程約40分鐘的咸德西牛峰海水浴場，由此展開一天。輕鬆享受翡翠綠的海水、白色沙灘與偶來19號路線的步行遺產後，動線便接續往內陸的城邑與東端的城山·萬丈窟。由於是上午較早的時段，即使在夏季旺季也相對清幽。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"hamdeok_seoubong_beach","kb_version":"1.19","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["Jeju Olle Foundation — Trail Course 19 official map","VisitJeju — Hamdeok Seoubong Beach","Jeju 4·3 Peace Foundation — Imperial Japanese Army tunnel records","Korea Tourism Organization — Top 3 Jeju Beaches ranking","Jocheon-eup local cultural office — Seoubong oreum trail records"]},"convenience":{"restroom":"海灘設有公共洗手間與淋浴設施","parking":"公共停車場（夏季收費）"},"smartNotes":{"photo":"夕陽搭配犀牛峰剪影是經典畫面；犀牛峰山頂俯瞰可拍下白沙灣的弧線","facilities":"海濱沿線有多家咖啡館；附近有便利商店","tip":"比起挾才或金寧海灘人潮少；東側 Delmoondo 咖啡館一帶是夕陽熱點"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"海灘 24 小時開放；管理開放游泳期為 7–8 月並配置救生員","closed":"全年開放","admission":"免費","walking":"難度輕鬆——海灘為平坦沙地；犀牛峰登山難度中等（含階梯）"},"images":["/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-01.webp","/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-02.webp","/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-04.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-01.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-02.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-04.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438.webp","location":"鹹德西牛峰海灘","caption":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — photo 1","alt":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-01.webp","location":"鹹德西牛峰海灘","caption":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — photo 2","alt":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-02.webp","location":"鹹德西牛峰海灘","caption":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — photo 3","alt":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/hamdeok-beach/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-04.webp","location":"鹹德西牛峰海灘","caption":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — photo 4","alt":"鹹德西牛峰海灘 — gallery image 4"}]},{"number":3,"time":"≈ 11:00","duration":"60分鐘","name":"城邑民俗村","category":"朝鮮時代城郭城鎮——重要民俗文化遺產（1423年創立）","description":"**城邑民俗村**是**朝鮮時代的城郭式城鎮，始建於1423年**，持續作為縣政中心**近500年，直至1914年**。村落在原有邑城範圍內保存著**110棟傳統建築**，被指定為**韓國重要民俗文化遺產**。村落中心聳立著**兩棵樹齡逾600年的天然紀念物古樹**。當地特色**五味子酒**可在村內家庭釀酒坊免費品嚐。韓劇**《大長今》（MBC，2003至2004年）**曾在此取景。**免費入場**；以戶外步行為主。","image":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","highlights":["**始建於1423年**——縣政中心持續運作至**1914年（近500年）**","保存**110棟傳統建築** + **韓國重要民俗文化遺產**","**兩棵樹齡逾600年天然紀念物古樹**矗立村落中心","**五味子酒** — 濟州傳統米釀酒，免費品嚐","**《大長今》（MBC 2003至2004年）**拍攝地","歷史傷痕：**1826年大火** + **1948年濟州四三事件**破壞","**免費入場** — 仍有約250戶人家居住","按照**朝鮮韓國風水原則**規劃，典型縣政中心格局","村落整體 + 多棟個別建築獲**獨立遺產指定**"],"timeUsed":["停車+村落解說員迎接簡介——約10分鐘","走至古樹+村落中心——約10分鐘","參觀韓屋內部（代表性民居2–3棟）——約15分鐘","五味子酒釀造坊免費品嚐——約10分鐘","奧萊小巷散步+拍照——約10分鐘","集合時間——約5分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"**今日行程唯一的內陸朝鮮時代遺產，也是地理上的轉折點。** 位於由咸德海岸前往城山的途中（表善內陸），將單純的行車時間轉化為有意義的停留。國家民俗文化財村落的石牆·茅草屋與600年古樹，與午後的火山·海女遺產形成對比，增添一段「悠閒的文化漫步」，讓一天不至於只流於拍照名勝的巡禮，取得平衡。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"seongeup_folk_village","kb_version":"1.19","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["Cultural Heritage Administration — Important Folklore Cultural Heritage designation","Korea Cultural Heritage Foundation — Seongeup Folk Village historical records","VisitJeju — Seongeup Minsok Maeul","MBC Drama Archive — Dae Jang Geum (2003–2004) filming locations","Jeju Folklore Society — Omegisul brewing tradition documentation"]},"smartNotes":{"photo":"Stone walls (dolhareubang grandfathers), thatched-roof houses with smoke holes, and traditional doors are iconic Jeju shots","facilities":"Visitor information center at entrance; English maps available","tip":"Hire a free volunteer guide at the entrance for cultural context; respect that residents actually live here — don''t enter homes uninvited"},"convenience":{"restroom":"Public restrooms at village entrance","parking":"Free parking near entrance"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"Open 24 hours (outdoor village); shops typically 09:00–17:00","closed":"Open year-round","admission":"Free for general village; some private homes charge for guided visits","walking":"Easy — flat dirt and stone paths through the village"},"images":["/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-38-22.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-26.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-11-12-24-47.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-38-22.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-26.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-11-12-24-47.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-37-51.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 1","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-38-22.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 2","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-26.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 3","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-42-34.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 4","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 4"},{"id":5,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongeup-folk-village/chatgpt-image-2026-5-11-12-24-47.webp","location":"城邑民俗村","caption":"城邑民俗村 — photo 6","alt":"城邑民俗村 — gallery image 6"}]},{"number":4,"time":"≈ 12:20","duration":"60分鐘","name":"午餐（濟州本地餐廳）","category":"午間休息——東濟州本地菜","description":"城邑民俗村與城山日出峰之間約60分鐘的午餐時間。可在城山邑港口周邊的餐廳品嚐黑豬肉、鮑魚石鍋、白帶魚等濟州東部的鄉土料理。午餐費用另計（約 ₩15,000）。","image":null,"highlights":["**冷湯生魚片（冷湯生魚片）**——東濟州地區特色料理","**鮑魚石鍋湯（鮑魚石鍋飯）**全年供應","**海膽麵（海膽面）**可選——東海岸招牌食材","城山邑定位——午餐後**10分鐘車程抵達城山日出峰**","午餐費用約**₩15,000**，現場自費","素食及清真餐需求請提前告知"],"timeUsed":["大巴前往午餐地點 — 約5分鐘","點餐 + 用餐 — 約45分鐘","大巴前往城山日出峰入口 — 約10分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"**聯合國教科文組織核心行程前的再充電。** 在由城邑前往城山途中的在地餐廳，以黑豬肉·鮑魚石鍋·當季海鮮等東濟州鄉土料理享用午餐（餐費另計）。這是在進入一天中最活躍的午後 — 城山登頂、海女潛水表演、萬丈窟 — 之前補充體力的時段。","smartNotes":{},"convenience":{},"visitBasics":{}},{"number":5,"time":"≈ 13:50","duration":"90分鐘","name":"城山日出峰","category":"UNESCO凝灰岩錐——日出峰（三重UNESCO認定）","description":"**城山日出峰（城山日出峰，「日出峰」）**是一座**距今5,000年的薩託謝安式水火山凝灰岩錐**，擁有**UNESCO三重認定**（世界遺產2007 + 生物圈保護區2002 + 全球地質公園2010）。火口**直徑600公尺、深90公尺**，周圍環繞著**99塊鋸齒狀邊緣岩石**。步道：**單程0.8公里，爬升約140公尺，來回60分鐘**，沿寬闊石階攀登。**海女表演**每日在峰下岩石海灣**14:00（每日1场）**各舉行一場（UNESCO非物質文化遺產2016年）。\n\n門票：**成人₩5,000 / 青少年₩2,500**，7歲以下及65歲以上免費。山頂是韓國**元旦日出朝聖**首選地——每年1月1日有逾5萬人在黎明前登頂。","image":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","highlights":["**UNESCO三重認定**：世界遺產2007 + 生物圈保護區2002 + 全球地質公園2010","**距今5,000年** — 薩託謝安式水火山噴發誕生","火口**直徑600公尺、深90公尺**，環繞著**99塊鋸齒狀邊緣岩石**（「石冠」）","**海拔182公尺** — 石階步道來回60分鐘","**每日14:00海女表演** — UNESCO非物質文化遺產2016年","門票：成人₩5,000 / 青少年₩2,500 / 7歲以下及65歲以上免費","春秋季開放時間 **05:00至19:00**（最後入場18:20）","**每月第一個星期一休館**","韓國**元旦日出朝聖**首選地，每年逾5萬人登頂"],"timeUsed":["停車+購票+底部簡介——約10分鐘","登頂觀景臺（0.8公里/高差140米）——約30分鐘","頂部觀景+火山口邊緣拍照——約20分鐘","下山——約20分鐘","可選：在底部觀看海女表演（每日1場，下午2點；惡劣天氣時可能取消）——約10分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"**一天兩處世界自然遺產的第一處。** 午餐後登上城山日出峰（選擇性登頂往返約30分鐘），觀賞約5,000年前由水中噴發隆起的凝灰岩錐。登頂後隨即銜接同一海域舉行的海女潛水表演，再以同屬2007年登錄資產的萬丈窟熔岩洞收尾，在一天之內完整「火山島與熔岩洞窟」的敘事。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"seongsan_ilchulbong","kb_version":"1.19","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["UNESCO WHC inscription 1264 (Jeju Volcanic Island and Lava Tubes, 2007-07-02)","UNESCO Global Geoparks Network — Jeju (2010-10 designation)","Cultural Heritage Administration — Natural Monument designation 2000-07-19","Seongsan Ilchulbong official site (seongsan.kr) — April 2025 admission update","Jeju Haenyeo Museum — UNESCO Intangible 2016 inscription record"]},"smartNotes":{"photo":"Summit view of Hallasan to the west and Udo island to the north on clear days; haenyeo black-sand beach view from descending path","facilities":"Café (Fritz Coffee 1.3km away has best exterior views of the peak); ferry to Udo Island from Seongsan Port (1.5km/15 min walk)","tip":"All stairs but well-maintained — manageable in casual clothes; family-friendly with rest stops; sunrise visits popular but crowds gather pre-dawn"},"convenience":{"restroom":"Available at entrance and base","parking":"Large free parking lot"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"Mar–Apr & Sep–Oct: 05:00–19:00; May–Aug: 04:30–20:00; Nov–Feb: 06:00–18:00 (last ticketing 1 hour before closing)","closed":"Open year-round (weather closures possible)","admission":"Adult 5,000 KRW / Youth & Child 2,500 KRW (VisitKorea reference)","walking":"Moderate — 20–30 min steady stair climb (≈ 600 stairs); benches every few minutes for rest"},"images":["/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-07.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-08.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-09.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-10.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/seongsan-haenyeo-show-ai.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-07.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-08.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-09.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-10.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/seongsan-haenyeo-show-ai.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-06.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 1","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-07.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 2","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-08.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 3","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-09.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 4","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 4"},{"id":5,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/kakaotalk-20260510-230028438-10.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 5","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 5"},{"id":6,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/photo-006.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 6","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 6"},{"id":7,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/seongsan-ilchulbong/seongsan-haenyeo-show-ai.webp","location":"城山日出峰","caption":"城山日出峰 — photo 12","alt":"城山日出峰 — gallery image 12"}],"liveStatusWidget":"haenyeo"},{"number":6,"time":"≈ 15:10","duration":"50分鐘","name":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","category":"聯合國教科文組織人類非物質文化遺產 — 濟州海女文化（2016）現場演出","description":"**濟州海女文化**是 **2016年列名聯合國教科文組織人類非物質文化遺產** 的活態遺產。本行程觀賞的並非博物館展示，而是 **在城山日出峰下的海域實地登場的海女潛水表演**。一輩子以大海為工作場域的 **高齡現役海女** 不使用氧氣裝備，僅憑 *tewak（浮標）* 浮力載浮載沉、潛入海底，並能親耳聽見她們結束潛水時吐出、宛如口哨般獨特的「숨비소리（喘息聲）」。\n\n表演通常 **每日兩場（約13:30·15:00）**，視海況與天候而定，**觀賞免費**。海女依深度與潛水能力分為 **下軍·中軍·上軍**，上軍能 **僅憑一次呼吸下潛10公尺以上**。目前現役海女 **不到4,000人，多數70歲以上**，因此親眼所見的每一幕潛水，都是這項漸漸消逝遺產的紀錄。\n\n**遇天候·浪況導致表演取消之日**，將改以位於舊左邑下道里的 **濟州海女博物館**（成人 ₩1,100，室內比例約80%，3個展廳）替代，在室內延續同一項聯合國教科文組織非物質遺產的深度體驗。","image":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","highlights":["**聯合國教科文組織人類非物質文化遺產（2016）** 以非博物館的形式呈現為 **現場潛水表演**","**在城山日出峰下的海域** 觀賞現役海女實際的潛水身影","不帶氧氣瓶、僅憑一個 *tewak（浮標）* — 上軍能 **一次呼吸下潛10公尺以上**","親耳聆聽潛水結束時獨特的 **喘息聲（숨비소리）**","表演通常 **每日2場（約13:30·15:00）**、**觀賞免費**，視天候·海況進行","現役海女 **不到4,000人·多數70歲以上** — 漸漸消逝的遺產","**表演取消時改為海女博物館**（成人 ₩1,100，室內80%，3個展廳）","與城山日出峰 **步行·車程5分鐘** — 動線零損失的自然銜接"],"timeUsed":["由城山日出峰前往表演場 — 約5分鐘","表演說明 + 就位 — 約5分鐘","觀賞海女潛水表演 — 約30分鐘","拍照 + 提問 — 約5分鐘","集合 + 移動緩衝 — 約5分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"**以「現場」而非「展示」邂逅聯合國教科文組織非物質遺產的高潮。** 結束城山日出峰的登頂與觀賞之後，自然地銜接至同一海域舉行的海女潛水表演（移動5分鐘）。用方才看過凝灰岩錐火山地質（世界自然遺產）的雙眼，緊接著欣賞在那片海域世代生活的海女非物質遺產（2016），這樣的構成完整了東部行程獨有的「火山 + 人」敘事。表演免費，且通常於午後時段舉行，與動線也相當契合。**唯因海況·天候可能取消**，遇此情形將改以下道里海女博物館的室內參觀替代，**確保無論何種天候都能體驗海女遺產**。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"jeju_haenyeo_museum","kb_version":"1.29","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage — Culture of Jeju Haenyeo (2016 inscription)","Jeju Haenyeo Museum official site (haenyeo.go.kr)","VisitJeju — Seongsan Haenyeo diving performance","Jeju Special Self-Governing Province — haenyeo population census records"]},"convenience":{"restroom":"表演場附近／博物館內多處","parking":"表演場·博物館皆免費停車"},"smartNotes":{"photo":"倚著浮標浮出水面的海女剪影，以及以城山日出峰為背景的海景，是最具象徵性的畫面。","facilities":"表演場附近的洗手間·停車／取消時可使用海女博物館的咖啡廳·紀念品店·英文導覽","tip":"表演時間會依當日海況變動，導遊將於現場說明。建議備好帽子·太陽眼鏡等防曬用品。"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"表演通常13:30·15:00（依當日海況·天候變動）／海女博物館09:00–18:00（最後入場17:00）","closed":"表演：天候·浪況時取消／博物館：星期一·1月1日·農曆新年·中秋公休","admission":"潛水表演觀賞免費／替代時海女博物館成人1,100韓元·青少年800韓元·兒童500韓元","walking":"輕鬆 — 於海岸觀賞，改為博物館時為配備電梯的室內"},"images":["/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-16.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-17.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-16.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-17.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-16.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 1","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-17.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 2","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/kakaotalk-20260510-230009595-18.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 3","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 3"},{"id":4,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-diving-ai.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 4","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 4"},{"id":5,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/jeju-haenyeo-museum/haenyeo-sunset-silhouette-ai.webp","location":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館）","caption":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — photo 5","alt":"海女潛水表演（表演取消時改為海女博物館） — gallery image 5"}]},{"number":7,"time":"≈ 16:30","duration":"55分鐘","name":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","category":"聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 — 拒文岳熔岩洞系統（2007年登錄）","description":"**萬丈窟（Manjanggul Lava Tube）**是約 **8,000年前由漢拏山側火山——拒文岳噴發的熔岩**所形成的熔岩洞，於 **2007年與城山日出峰、漢拏山一同以「濟州火山島與熔岩洞窟」之名登錄為聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產**。萬丈窟與城山日出峰同屬 **同一項單一登錄資產**，因此本行程在一天之內就能同時納入 **兩處世界自然遺產**。\n\n全長約 **7.4公里**（含連接區段時為13〜15公里），屬世界最大級的熔岩洞，主通道達 **寬18公尺·高23〜25公尺**。由天花板塌陷形成的三個入口中，**僅第二入口約1公里區段對一般遊客開放**，採進入後沿原路折返的 **往返約30〜45分鐘** 路線。開放區段盡頭佇立著 **高7.6公尺、世界最大的熔岩石柱**，是萬丈窟的代表性拍照景點。\n\n洞內 **全年維持11〜13℃**，夏季沁涼、冬季溫暖，但洞底昏暗且略為潮濕，建議備好 **外套與防滑鞋**。萬丈窟同時也被指定為 **國家天然紀念物**。門票為 **成人 ₩4,000（團體 ₩3,000）／青少年·兒童 ₩2,000**，營運時間 **09:00〜18:00（最後入場17:10）**，每月第一個星期三公休。","image":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","highlights":["**2007年聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產** — 與城山日出峰同屬「濟州火山島與熔岩洞窟」登錄","**一天參觀兩處世界自然遺產** — 城山日出峰 + 萬丈窟","全長約 **7.4公里**，開放區段約 **1公里**（往返約30〜45分鐘）","開放區段盡頭 **高7.6公尺、世界最大熔岩石柱**","主通道 **寬18公尺 · 高23〜25公尺** — 世界最大級熔岩洞","**拒文岳熔岩洞系統** — 約8,000年前形成，國家天然紀念物","洞內 **全年11〜13℃** — 夏季避暑勝地，建議帶外套","門票 **成人 ₩4,000 ／青少年·兒童 ₩2,000**，營運 **09:00〜18:00（最後入場17:10）**"],"timeUsed":["停車 + 購票 + 入場 — 約5分鐘","第二入口下行 + 進入洞窟 — 約5分鐘","開放區段1公里往返（至熔岩石柱）— 約30分鐘","遊客中心熔岩洞形成解說 — 約10分鐘","集合 + 移動緩衝 — 約5分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"**今日行程的第二處聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產，也是自然壓軸。** 在走過城山日出峰（三重聯合國教科文組織認定的凝灰岩錐）與海女潛水表演（非物質文化遺產）之後，位於金寧的萬丈窟自然落在由城山返回濟州市的動線上。由於它與城山日出峰同屬 **2007年的單一登錄資產**，將兩處串在一天之內，便能完整呈現「火山島與熔岩洞窟」的聯合國教科文組織敘事。安排在午後時段，可 **避開正午的暑熱與團體人潮**，並在戶外行程之後於 **全年11〜13℃的清涼洞窟** 中為一天收尾，營造舒適的節奏。若萬丈窟因維護整修或天候而關閉，將以同屬一熔岩洞系統的 **日出樂園美川窟** 替代，維持洞窟體驗。","_poi_meta":{"poi_key":"manjanggul_lava_tube","kb_version":"1.29","verified_date":"2026-04-29","sources":["visitjeju.net (Visit Jeju official)","english.visitkorea.or.kr","jeju.go.kr/geopark","UNESCO Jeju Volcanic Island and Lava Tubes (whc.unesco.org)","Wikipedia Manjanggul (Dec 2025)"]},"convenience":{"restroom":"入口遊客中心設有洗手間","parking":"入口免費停車場"},"smartNotes":{"photo":"開放區段盡頭 **高7.6公尺、世界最大的熔岩石柱** 是代表性畫面，朝寬18公尺·高23公尺長通道拍攝的透視照同樣以氣勢取勝。","facilities":"入口停車場旁的遊客中心會說明熔岩洞的形成過程 — 建議入場前花10分鐘參觀。洞內沒有販賣部。","tip":"即使夏季也請帶上外套（洞內11〜13℃）。洞底潮濕昏暗，建議穿防滑鞋。萬丈窟可能因維護整修而關閉，請提前確認當日是否營運。"},"visitBasics":{"hours":"09:00〜18:00（最後入場17:10）","closed":"每月第一個星期三／豪雨時臨時休館","admission":"成人4,000韓元（團體3,000韓元）／青少年·兒童2,000韓元（團體1,500韓元）","walking":"適中 — 平坦的1公里往返，洞口需下階梯，洞底略為崎嶇潮濕"},"images":["/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp"],"imageCredits":[{"url":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","source":"atoc-korea"},{"url":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp","source":"atoc-korea"}],"galleryItems":[{"id":1,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-08.webp","location":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — photo 1","alt":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 1"},{"id":2,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-22.webp","location":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — photo 2","alt":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 2"},{"id":3,"type":"photo","src":"/images/tours/ilchulland/chatgpt-image-2026-5-8-07-49-24.webp","location":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞）","caption":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — photo 3","alt":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 · 熔岩洞） — gallery image 3"}]},{"number":8,"time":"≈ 17:45","duration":"30分鐘","name":"下車（2個地點+東門市場）","category":"下車——濟州市集散點順序","description":"**濟州市三個下車點，方便返回飯店或晚餐**。下車點：濟州市政廳∕涯月洞（約17:30至18:00）→ 濟州機場（約17:40）→ 東門傳統市場（約18:00）。東門傳統市場下車後可自行前往晚餐（司機不陪同進入市場）；黑豬肉街距東門步行約5分鐘。機場下車適合當晚有晚班機的旅客（濟州國際機場末班機約21:30，17:40下車後時間充裕）。","image":null,"highlights":["三個下車點：**市政廳∕涯月洞（≈17:30–18:00）→ 機場（≈17:40）→ 東門市場（≈18:00）**","**機場下車（≈17:40）**——末班機前充裕時間辦理登機","**東門傳統市場**下車後可步行至**黑豬肉街（約5分鐘）**","下車後為自由時間，司機不陪同"],"timeUsed":["大巴海女博物館 → 東門 — 約25分鐘","東門傳統市場下車 — 5分鐘","大巴前往市政府 — 約10分鐘","市政府下車 — 5分鐘","大巴前往機場 — 約15分鐘","機場下車 — 5分鐘"],"whyOnRoute":"東門市場下車 = 可選的晚餐停留。市政廳＋機場覆蓋飯店區及晚班機旅客。距海女博物館至機場約40分鐘車程。","smartNotes":{},"convenience":{},"visitBasics":{},"_role":"dropoff"}]}},{"id":"day_flow","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourDayFlowSection","props":{"routeFlowStops":[{"name":"濟州市+機場接送","type":"origin","theme":"出發"},{"name":"鹹德西牛峰海灘","type":"secondary","theme":"海灘"},{"name":"城邑民俗村","type":"primary","theme":"傳統村落"},{"name":"午餐","type":"meal","theme":"餐飲"},{"name":"城山日出峰（UNESCO）","type":"primary","theme":"UNESCO火山"},{"name":"海女潛水表演","type":"primary","theme":"海女非物質遺產"},{"name":"萬丈窟（聯合國教科文組織）","type":"primary","theme":"聯合國教科文組織熔岩洞"},{"name":"濟州市下車","type":"return","theme":"返回"}],"routePhases":[{"phase":"接送與海岸出發","duration":"約1小時","description":"濟州市4個地點接送（08:30〜09:05）後前往咸德西牛峰海水浴場。"},{"phase":"由海岸前往內陸文化遺產","duration":"約2小時","description":"咸德西牛峰海水浴場（60分鐘）→ 城邑民俗村（朝鮮時代國家民俗文化財，60分鐘）。"},{"phase":"午餐","duration":"約1小時","description":"城山附近的在地餐廳 — 黑豬肉、鮑魚石鍋、當季海鮮。午餐費用另計。"},{"phase":"聯合國教科文組織核心","duration":"約3小時","description":"城山日出峰（選擇性登頂）→ 海女潛水表演（取消時改為海女博物館）→ 萬丈窟熔岩洞（聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產）。"},{"phase":"返程","duration":"約1小時","description":"金寧 → 前往濟州市 + 2個地點及東門市場下車。"}],"routeShapeIntro":{"title":"行程路線一覽","subtitle":"這是一條由東端在一天之內串起島上兩處聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產的東濟州環線 — 城山日出峰（凝灰岩錐）與萬丈窟（熔岩洞），兩者皆於2007年以同一資產登錄。再加上聯合國教科文組織非物質遺產的海女潛水表演。以高效率的行程避開主要景點的人潮。"}}},{"id":"details","section_html_id":"details","component":"TourFitSection","props":{"whyTourWorks":{"bestFor":["初次遊覽該地區的旅客","情侶","成人家庭","能夠應付全日活躍行程的旅客","希望參觀UNESCO世界遺產景點的旅客"],"lessIdealFor":["希望步行量最少的旅客","攜帶嬰兒車的親子團","當天還要趕航班的旅客"],"routeLogicSections":[{"title":"為何如此安排路線","icon":"route","iconBg":"bg-sky-50/80","iconColor":"text-sky-600","items":[{"label":"一天參觀2處聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產 + 非物質遺產","detail":"城山日出峰與萬丈窟是2007年以「濟州火山島與熔岩洞窟」一同登錄的世界自然遺產。再加上2016年人類非物質文化遺產的海女潛水表演，一天之內便能看見三重的聯合國教科文組織遺產。"},{"label":"真正的萬丈窟 — 不再是替代景點，而是原汁原味的聯合國教科文組織熔岩洞","detail":"過去休館期間曾以美川窟替代，如今則親自探訪世界最大級的熔岩洞、擁有高7.6公尺世界最大熔岩石柱的萬丈窟。"},{"label":"含全部門票 — 此價位的價值所在","detail":"城山日出峰 ₩5,000 + 萬丈窟 ₩4,000（城邑免費、海女潛水表演免費）— 僅 ₩9,000 門票便涵蓋兩處世界自然遺產。"},{"label":"城山日出峰為選擇性登頂","detail":"往返約30分鐘的火山口邊緣登頂有坡度，並非適合所有人。另有無需階梯、能享受相似景致的海岸環行步道，可依體力自行選擇。"}]}]}}},{"id":"practical","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourPracticalDetails","props":{"practicalAccordionItems":[{"id":"inclusions","title":"費用包含項目","preview":"全含入場費——此價位的最大優勢","content":["空調小型巴士、英語∕中文雙語認證導遊、全景點門票（城山日出峰₩5,000、城邑民俗村免費、日出樂園∕彌天窟₩12,000、海女博物館₩1,100、含德海灘免費）、燃料∕過路費∕停車費。","不含：午餐（約₩15,000）、飲料、小費。"]},{"id":"pickup","title":"接送與下車地點","preview":"四個順序接送點；**機場使用1號門**","content":["四個接送點順序：Ocean Suites濟州（08:30）→ 濟州機場1號門1樓國內入境廳（08:45，注意：東部行程使用1號門）→ LOTTE City Hotel濟州（08:55）→ 新羅免稅店濟州（09:05）。","預訂時選擇最近的接送點。","出發前一天透過WhatsApp確認行程。"]},{"id":"walking","title":"步行強度與地形","preview":"中等難度。","content":["中等難度。","咸德海灘為平坦沙地。","城邑民俗村為土路與石牆。","城山日出峰火山口邊緣登頂約30分鐘陡峭石階（可略過）。","海女潛水表演於平坦的海岸觀賞。","萬丈窟為約1公里平坦往返，洞口階梯與洞內略為崎嶇·潮濕的地面（全年11〜13℃，建議帶外套）。","務必穿著包覆腳趾的鞋子。","總步行約4〜5公里。"]},{"id":"cancellation","title":"取消政策","preview":"接送前24小時可免費取消","content":["接送前24小時可免費取消。","當天取消及無故缺席不予退款。","大風天氣可能縮短城山登頂，但不取消全日行程。"]},{"id":"cave","title":"洞窟須知（萬丈窟）","preview":"萬丈窟為聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產熔岩洞，已包含於行程中。","content":["萬丈窟為2007年登錄的聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產熔岩洞，已包含於本行程中。","開放區段約1公里往返（約30〜45分鐘），盡頭有高7.6公尺、世界最大的熔岩石柱。","洞內全年11〜13℃，相當清涼，建議帶外套。","若因維護整修或天候而關閉，可能改以鄰近熔岩洞（日出樂園美川窟）替代 — 請於預訂時確認。"]},{"id":"children","title":"兒童與無障礙","preview":"建議10歲或以上，因為城山日出峰約600級石階","content":["建議10歲或以上，因為城山日出峰的火山口邊緣登頂（約600級石階，可選但為全日核心亮點）及9小時全日節奏。","較小的孩子可以參加，但登頂可能太吃力；建議改選年度賞花或郵輪巴士行程（不含登頂）。","城山石階及城邑民俗村步道不推薦嬰兒車。"]}],"practicalWeatherStatic":{"today":{"temp":"—","label":"即時天氣連動"},"tomorrow":{"temp":"—","label":"每日更新"},"_seasonalSummary":"東濟州擁有全島最通透的海景，夏季氣溫也是全島最高。城山日出峰全年風力較強，建議備一件薄外套。","_seasonalTemperatures":[{"season":"春季（3至5月）","range":"8–22°C","notes":"四月初賞櫻；含德犀牛峰斜坡油菜花盛開。"},{"season":"夏季（6至8月）","range":"22–30°C","notes":"炎熱但海岸景點有海風。含德海灘海水色彩最佳。"},{"season":"秋季（9至11月）","range":"10–24°C","notes":"最佳季節——城山日出峰山脊視野最為清晰。"},{"season":"冬季（12至2月）","range":"3–10°C","notes":"城山日出峰山脊風寒效應明顯。各景點人潮最少。"}]},"seasonalVariations":[{"season":"春季","description":"含德犀牛峰斜坡的油菜（蕓薹）花——翠綠海水映襯金黃花海。"},{"season":"夏季","description":"含德海灘海水色彩最佳；城山日出峰日照時間充足。"},{"season":"秋季","description":"城山日出峰山脊全景視野最為清晰；城邑民俗村全年最具攝影價值。"},{"season":"冬季","description":"遊客最少；海女博物館在寒天尤為珍貴。"}]}},{"id":"booking_support","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourBookingSupportSection","props":{"bookingTrustItems":[{"icon":"check-circle","title":"當地持照合法業者","description":"持牌韓國旅遊合作業者，備有完整保險","iconBg":"bg-emerald-50/80","iconColor":"text-emerald-600","body":"持牌韓國旅遊合作業者，備有完整保險"},{"icon":"route","title":"路線專家","description":"精心構成的行程，而非千篇一律的路線","iconBg":"bg-sky-50/80","iconColor":"text-sky-600","body":"行程費用已含全部門票：城山日出峰（₩5,000）、萬丈窟（₩4,000）、城邑民俗村（免費）、海女潛水表演（免費）— 現場無需另行支付任何項目。"},{"icon":"users","title":"精心控制團體人數","description":"精準控制人數的小型巴士格式","iconBg":"bg-amber-50/80","iconColor":"text-amber-600","body":"以小團體迷你巴士（最多14人）從容遊覽城邑巷弄、萬丈窟熔岩洞與海女潛水表演。"}],"bookingSupportSteps":[{"timing":"即時通知","title":"即時確認","detail":"您將收到含行程摘要的預訂確認通知。","description":"您將收到含行程摘要的預訂確認通知。"},{"timing":"出發前12小時","title":"出發前12小時提醒","detail":"出發前分享天氣更新及任何路線調整。","description":"出發前分享天氣更新及任何路線調整。"},{"timing":"前一晚","title":"最終接送資訊","detail":"確認確切接送時間及司機∕導遊聯絡方式。","description":"確認確切接送時間及司機∕導遊聯絡方式。"},{"timing":"行程當天早晨","title":"當日路線說明","detail":"出發當天早上根據最新現場狀況提供簡報。","description":"出發當天早上根據最新現場狀況提供簡報。"},{"timing":"行程途中","title":"景點逐一說明","detail":"每個景點提供即時現場導覽。","description":"每個景點提供即時現場導覽。"},{"timing":"行程結束後","title":"行程後支援","detail":"行程結束後提供後續建議及額外資訊。","description":"行程結束後提供後續建議及額外資訊。"}]}},{"id":"faq","section_html_id":"faq","component":"TourFaqSection","props":{"staticQuestions":[{"id":"q1","question":"真的能看到海女潛水表演嗎？","answer":"可以。行程包含於城山日出峰附近海域舉行的海女潛水表演觀賞（通常於午後，免費）。表演可能因海況與天候而取消，取消時將改以下道里海女博物館的室內參觀替代，確保海女遺產的體驗。"},{"id":"q2","question":"可以略過城山日出峰的火山口登頂嗎？","answer":"可以。另有無需階梯、也能享受相似拍照角度的海岸環行步道。火山口登頂（往返約0.8公里、約30分鐘）為選擇性項目，可依體力決定。"},{"id":"q3","question":"與濟州南部聯合國教科文組織行程有何不同？","answer":"為同一旅行社的行程。南部行程包含漢拏山오름、山茶花山丘、天帝淵瀑布、柱狀節理、Osulloc茶園。東部行程則以城山日出峰、城邑民俗村、萬丈窟、海女潛水表演為主進行。"},{"id":"q4","question":"萬丈窟關閉的日子會如何安排？","answer":"萬丈窟為聯合國教科文組織世界自然遺產熔岩洞，已包含於行程中。唯遇維護整修或天候（豪雨等）而關閉之日，將以同屬一熔岩洞系統的日出樂園美川窟等鄰近洞窟替代，維持洞窟體驗。"},{"id":"q5","question":"有包含午餐嗎？","answer":"不包含。午餐費用另計（約 ₩15,000），導遊會為您介紹在地美食。"}]}},{"id":"reviews","section_html_id":"reviews","component":"TourReviewsSection","props":{"guestReviews":[],"reviewsSummary":{"averageRating":0,"totalReviews":0,"ratingDistribution":[{"stars":5,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":4,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":3,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":2,"count":0,"percentage":0},{"stars":1,"count":0,"percentage":0}],"highlights":[]},"reviewsAttribution":"綜合評價來自業者在 市場參考資料 上的商品頁；個別評論可於該平台查看。"}},{"id":"sticky_booking","section_html_id":null,"component":"TourStickyBookingBar","props":{"note":"可訂狀態會在付款步驟中確認。","price":{"amountLabel":"47","originalPriceUsd":59,"salePriceUsd":47,"discountPercent":20,"currency":"USD","per":"person"}}}],"itinerary_variants":[],"_publication":{"schema_version":"v4_canonical","last_modified":"2026-04-28","version_history":["v11","v12","v13","v14","v15","v15.2"],"fix_passes":{"v12":"P0+P1 — pickup_dropoff Schema A unification, routeFlowStops type-based, competing_products → internal slugs, anchor_poi_keys aligned","v13":"P1.5 — pickup_dropoff Schema A.2 → A.1; practicalAccordionItems / routePhases / seasonalVariations unified to V4 canonical (no Tailwind in data)","v14":"P2 — _publication uniform; duration formatting standardized; glanceItems Duration added where missing","v15":"P3 round 1 — SEO trim. seo.pageTitle rewritten to ≤65 chars (was 14/25 over 70); seo.metaDescription rewritten to ≤168 chars (was 25/25 over 170). primaryKeywords and ogImage unchanged. Hero/OG images, POI verification, review imports, and routePhases enrichment deferred to later P3 rounds.","v15.2_charter_consolidation":"Removed \"jeju-popular-sightseeing-private-car-charter-tour\" from competing_products per Jason''s one-charter-per-region rule (jeju-island-private-car-charter-tour remains as canonical Jeju charter).","v17_schema_unification":{"date":"2026-04-28","description":"Phase 1: Standardized matching_profile scores to the current 0-1 float scale used by match_tours.matching_profile.","fields_converted":43,"fields_skipped":0,"fields_already_float":0},"v17_batch2_enhancement":{"date":"2026-04-28","description":"Batch 2 deep enhancement — descriptions raised to 700-1100+ chars; KB-backed visitBasics/convenience/smartNotes/_poi_meta on all attraction stops; product profile recalibrated with verified-fact 0-1 float scores (replacing Phase 1 mechanical conversion).","_score_audit":{"_methodology":"0-1 float scale. Each score grounded in verified facts.","deltas_applied":{"unesco_fit":{"old":1,"new":1,"reasoning":"VERIFIED 1.0 — this tour is correctly named ''eastern UNESCO loop'': Seongsan = UNESCO World Heritage (Jeju Volcanic Island & Lava Tubes 2007), Haenyeo Museum = UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage (haenyeo culture 2016). Tour covers BOTH UNESCO categories. Strongest UNESCO-fit tour in catalogue."},"intangible_heritage_fit":{"old":1,"new":1,"reasoning":"VERIFIED 1.0 — Haenyeo Museum is the dedicated UNESCO ICH interpretation center; Seongsan haenyeo demonstration at 14:00 (1 show/day) is the live UNESCO ICH performance; Seongeup Folk Village preserves Joseon-period intangible folkways. 3 of 5 attractions carry intangible-heritage value. Highest possible score."},"walking_level":{"old":0.8,"new":0.65,"reasoning":"DOWNGRADED 0.8→0.65 with verified totals: Hamdeok beach 0.5 km flat (sand + boardwalk), Seongeup ~1 km flat olle, Micheon Cave 365 m flat (leveled), Seongsan 0.8 km + 140 m gain (the only stair-heavy stop), Haenyeo Museum 100% indoor flat. Total ~3 km + only Seongsan has elevation. Tour 1 (east-signature) walks more (Seopjikoji 2.1 km extra). Verified moderate walking = 0.65 not 0.8."},"young_kids_fit":{"old":1,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"DOWNGRADED 1.0→0.75: Hamdeok beach + leveled Micheon Cave + indoor Haenyeo Museum + Seongeup folk village = 4 of 5 kid-friendly. ONLY Seongsan''s 300-500 steps challenge under-7s. Mechanical 1.0 was overstated; verified 0.75 is honest."},"stroller_fit":{"old":0.4,"new":0.5,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.4→0.50: Hamdeok flat + Micheon Cave LEVELED FLOOR (verified — vs Manjanggul''s uneven natural floor) + Haenyeo Museum 100% accessible + Seongeup main alleys + ONLY Seongsan stairs unsuitable. 4/5 stroller-friendly = 0.50 not the previous 0.4. Specifically chose Micheon vs Manjanggul for accessibility."},"mobility_friendly_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.65,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.65: Verified 4 of 5 stops mobility-friendly (Hamdeok flat, Micheon leveled, Haenyeo Museum elevators, Seongeup flat alleys), only Seongsan summit not accessible. The choice of Micheon Cave instead of Manjanggul specifically supports this."},"weather_sensitivity":{"old":1,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"DOWNGRADED 1.0→0.75 — verified: Haenyeo Museum 100% indoor, Micheon Cave 100% indoor and stable temperature year-round, Seongeup hanok have shelter. Only Hamdeok and Seongsan are weather-exposed. The ''all UNESCO'' name made the prior score look high, but indoor ratio is actually reasonable. Mechanical 1.0 overstated."},"indoor_ratio":{"old":0.1,"new":0.4,"reasoning":"MAJOR CORRECTION: Verified breakdown — Hamdeok 100% outdoor, Seongeup ~30% indoor (visiting hanok interiors), Micheon Cave 100% indoor, Seongsan 5% indoor (visitor center only), Haenyeo Museum 100% indoor. Time-weighted indoor ratio ~40%, NOT the previous 10%. Correcting a documentation error."},"rain_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.75: With Micheon Cave (indoor), Haenyeo Museum (indoor), and Seongeup hanok interiors as rain refuges, this tour holds up MUCH better in rain than the mechanical 0.6 implied. Hamdeok and Seongsan suffer in rain but the rest is fine. Verified."},"iconic_landmark_fit":{"old":1,"new":0.85,"reasoning":"VERIFIED 0.85: Seongsan = universally iconic (triple UNESCO crown). Hamdeok = Top 3 Jeju beach. Seongeup + Haenyeo Museum = nationally significant culture (UNESCO ICH for Haenyeo). Micheon Cave = secondary lava tube. 0.85 — strong but not all 5 universally iconic."},"value_for_money_fit":{"old":1,"new":0.85,"reasoning":"Verified fees: Hamdeok free + Seongeup free + Micheon ₩12,000 + Seongsan ₩2,000 + Haenyeo Museum ₩1,100 = ~₩15,100/adult. Reasonable but Ilchul Land at ₩12,000 is the big driver. 0.85 calibrated."},"senior_fit":{"old":0.4,"new":0.55,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.4→0.55: With Hamdeok beach walk (flat), Micheon leveled cave, Seongeup flat alleys, Haenyeo Museum accessible — 4 of 5 stops fully senior-accessible. Only Seongsan summit excludes seniors with mobility issues (alternative: stay at base for haenyeo demo). Verified ≥0.55, much better than 0.4."},"senior_active_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.75,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.75: For active seniors, all 5 stops are achievable (Seongsan rest stops + benches make 45-60 min summit reasonable). Cultural depth (UNESCO + 600-year village + 400-year haenyeo tradition) very strong appeal for senior travelers. 0.75 verified."},"senior_general_fit":{"old":0.4,"new":0.55,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.4→0.55: Same logic — 4/5 stops accessible to general senior population (alternative for Seongsan = stay at base for haenyeo demonstration). 0.55 calibrated."},"beach_fit":{"old":0.6,"new":0.85,"reasoning":"UPGRADED 0.6→0.85: Hamdeok IS the dedicated beach stop — Top 3 Jeju beach (verified VisitKorea ranking). 0.6 understates this; 0.85 reflects beach as a primary tour theme."},"culture_level":{"old":1,"new":0.95,"reasoning":"Slight DOWNGRADE 1.0→0.95: Verified 3 strong cultural anchors (Seongeup 600-year town + Haenyeo 400-year tradition + Seongsan haenyeo demo). Hamdeok is recreational not cultural. 0.95 (vs east-signature''s lower) — still very strong."}}},"stops_enhanced":6,"sources":["VisitKorea","Wikipedia","UNESCO","Visit Jeju","Inside Jeju","Jeju Tourism Organization","AllTrails"]},"v17_fix1_indoor_ratio_correction":{"date":"2026-04-28","description":"Jason correction: Micheon Cave and Seongeup Folk Village are 70% outdoor. Recalculated tour-level indoor_ratio with time-weighted attraction durations and adjusted dependent fields.","computation":{"stops_time_weighted":{"hamdeok_seoubong_beach":"45min × 0.00 indoor = 0.00","seongeup_folk_village":"75min × 0.30 indoor = 22.50 (corrected from 0.50)","ilchulland_micheon_cave":"60min × 0.30 indoor = 18.00 (corrected from 0.60)","seongsan_ilchulbong":"90min × 0.05 indoor = 4.50","jeju_haenyeo_museum":"60min × 1.00 indoor = 60.00","total_indoor_min":105,"total_substantive_min":330,"computed_indoor_ratio":0.32}},"changes":{"indoor_ratio":{"old":0.4,"new":0.3,"reason":"Recalculated 105/330 = 0.32, rounded to 0.30"},"rain_fit":{"old":0.75,"new":0.55,"reason":"Only Haenyeo Museum is full refuge; Seongeup and Micheon mostly outdoor; Hamdeok and Seongsan rain-bad"},"weather_sensitivity":{"old":0.75,"new":0.7,"reason":"Still has Haenyeo Museum as anchor refuge but 70% of stop time is weather-exposed"}}}}},"liveStatusSection":"haenyeo"}'::jsonb
